\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 5238, \"to\": 5253}, {\"ngram\": \"the undetected beginning\", \"from\": 5267, \"to\": 5291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI see myself as a 19-year-old kid, sitting on a dais in a media room looking at a sea of adults,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she recalls.\", \"from\": 5321, \"to\": 5436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 19-year-old kid\", \"from\": 5340, \"to\": 5357}, {\"ngram\": \"a dais\", \"from\": 5370, \"to\": 5376}, {\"ngram\": \"a media room\", \"from\": 5380, \"to\": 5392}, {\"ngram\": \"a sea\", \"from\": 5404, \"to\": 5409}, {\"ngram\": \"adults\", \"from\": 5413, \"to\": 5419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAnd I am asking myself,Is anyone thinking what I am thinking?The only thing I could do is trust the system, as a 19-year-old kid.\", \"from\": 5437, \"to\": 5569, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 5466, \"to\": 5472}, {\"ngram\": \"thinking?The\", \"from\": 5492, \"to\": 5504}, {\"ngram\": \"only thing\", \"from\": 5505, \"to\": 5515}, {\"ngram\": \"the system\", \"from\": 5536, \"to\": 5546}, {\"ngram\": \"a 19-year-old kid\", \"from\": 5551, \"to\": 5568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People still say to me, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098You should have two more gold medals.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Twenty years after Sanders was left to wonder what was going on, 16-year-old Ye Shiwen of China won the 400 IM at the London Olympics and broke the world record by more than a second in the process.\", \"from\": 5570, \"to\": 5840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5661, \"end\": 5668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernie_Sanders\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4490235184802963e-38, \"text\": \"Sanders\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernie_Sanders\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernie_Sanders\"}, {\"begin\": 5719, \"end\": 5728, \"title\": \"http://d