ram\": \"Beisel\", \"from\": 7628, \"to\": 7634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI had many people come up to me after that race.\", \"from\": 7648, \"to\": 7699, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many people\", \"from\": 7657, \"to\": 7668}, {\"ngram\": \"that race\", \"from\": 7689, \"to\": 7698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Ye Shiwen never tested positive and I would never accuse her of anything.\", \"from\": 7700, \"to\": 7777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7704, \"end\": 7713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ye_Shiwen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ye Shiwen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ye_Shiwen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ye_Shiwen\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 7768, \"to\": 7776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I believe the results were fair, because there is no evidence they were not.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Says fellow 2012 Olympian Caitlin Leverenz Smith, who took bronze in the 200 IM that Ye won: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIn 2012 there were eyebrows being raised, and if anything it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s gotten worse.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d For evidence of that, skip ahead to the athlete dining hall at the World Aquatics Championships in Gwangju, South Korea, in 2019.\", \"from\": 7778, \"to\": 8167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7885, \"end\": 7901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Leverenz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caitlin Leverenz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Leverenz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Leverenz\"}, {\"begin\": 7944, \"end\": 7946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.990662052550034e-58, \"text\": \"Ye\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kanye_West\"}, {\"begin\": 8137, \"end\": 8144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gwangju\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.517552648692656e-31, \"text\": \"Gwangju\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gwangju\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gwangju\"}, {\"begin\": 8146, \"end\": 8157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9999999965075403, \"rank\": 3.4932746916117104e-09, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 7788, \"to\": 7799}, {\"ngram\": \"no evidence\", \"from\": 7828, \"to\": 7839}, {\"ngram\": \"not.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 7850, \"to\": 7857}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 7917, \"to\": 7923}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200 IM\", \"from\": 7927, \"to\": 7937}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIn\", \"from\": 7951, \"to\": 7956}, {\"ngram\": \"eyebrows\", \"from\": 7973, \"to\": 7981}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 8003, \"to\": 8011}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 8012, \"to\": 8018}, {\"ngram\": \"worse.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 8026, \"to\": 8035}, {\"ngram\": \"evidence\", \"from\": 8040, \"to\": 8048}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete dining hall\", \"from\": 8072, \"to\": 8095}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Aquatics Championships\", \"from\": 8099, \"to\": 8131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And a round of applause.\", \"from\": 8168, \"to\": 8192, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"And a round\", \"from\": 8168, \"to\": 8179}, {\"ngram\": \"applause\", \"from\": 8183, \"to\": 8191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sun Yang, the most famous and accomplished swimmer in Chinese history, had won the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 400-meter freestyle for the fourth straight time at the world championships.\", \"from\": 8194, \"to\": 8361, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8194, \"end\": 8202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yang\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sun Yang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yang\"}, {\"begin\": 8248, \"end\": 8263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_China\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chinese history\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most famous and accomplished swimmer\", \"from\": 8204, \"to\": 8244}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 400-meter freestyle\", \"from\": 8273, \"to\": 8304}, {\"ngram\": \"the fourth straight time\", \"from\": 8309, \"to\": 8333}, {\"ngram\": \"the world championships\", \"from\": 8337, \"to\": 8360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the post-race medal ceremony, Australian silver medalist Mack Horton refused to stand on the podium next to Sun, whose career had been steeped in controversy.\", \"from\": 8362, \"to\": 8523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8395, \"end\": 8405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9996812697272672, \"rank\": 0.0003188275115399245, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 8422, \"end\": 8433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mack_Horton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mack Horton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mack_Horton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mack_Horton\"}, {\"begin\": 8473, \"end\": 8476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Media\", \"score\