y.\", \"from\": 12368, \"to\": 12430, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 12396, \"to\": 12406}, {\"ngram\": \"your body\", \"from\": 12420, \"to\": 12429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That goes for multivitamins and any supplements you might take.\", \"from\": 12431, \"to\": 12494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"multivitamins\", \"from\": 12445, \"to\": 12458}, {\"ngram\": \"any supplements\", \"from\": 12463, \"to\": 12478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You give up an element of privacy and autonomy for the sake of integrity in sport.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Athletes who are in the testing pool are required to document their whereabouts 24 hours per day via online forms.\", \"from\": 12495, \"to\": 12696, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an element\", \"from\": 12507, \"to\": 12517}, {\"ngram\": \"privacy\", \"from\": 12521, \"to\": 12528}, {\"ngram\": \"autonomy\", \"from\": 12533, \"to\": 12541}, {\"ngram\": \"the sake\", \"from\": 12546, \"to\": 12554}, {\"ngram\": \"integrity\", \"from\": 12558, \"to\": 12567}, {\"ngram\": \"sport.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Athletes\", \"from\": 12571, \"to\": 12589}, {\"ngram\": \"the testing pool\", \"from\": 12601, \"to\": 12617}, {\"ngram\": \"their whereabouts\", \"from\": 12643, \"to\": 12660}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 12674, \"to\": 12677}, {\"ngram\": \"online forms\", \"from\": 12682, \"to\": 12694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If testers show up to administer random tests where the athlete says he or she will be and they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re not present, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a violation.\", \"from\": 12697, \"to\": 12830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"testers\", \"from\": 12700, \"to\": 12707}, {\"ngram\": \"random tests\", \"from\": 12730, \"to\": 12742}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 12749, \"to\": 12760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three whereabouts violations can count as a positive drug test and lead to sanctions.\", \"from\": 12831, \"to